Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeglobalexpression.rst
Summary: A visual shader node that allows referencing global variables in shader graphs.

Inherits: VisualShaderNode < VisualShaderNodeExpression < VisualShaderNode
Note: This node is used in the Visual Shader Graph to reference global variables defined in the project.
